    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction is accepted as a complete and documented assessment package. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors have been formally assessed; six remain not-assessed due to resource and data limitations. The provenance chain supporting the hemolysis index validation result is considered internally consistent. The package is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier with the understanding that the Not Accepted decision outcome reflects model inadequacy, not assessment incompleteness.",
